{"tid":769262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羽毛球世錦／包辦女雙冠亞軍　日本國旗南京升起！陸網友崩潰","createTime":"2018-08-06T04:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T09:27:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":409,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"8570a9c13e53558bb72a15133eeeec299bebb28a","tid":769262,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n2018年羽球世錦賽在中國大陸南京舉辦，今年的羽球女雙，冠亞軍都是由日本隊包下。在舉行頒獎典禮，現場奏起了日本國歌並升起了三面日本國旗，沒想到此舉卻讓中國大陸的網友都崩潰了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1477692-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1477692-XXL.jpg&h=11866802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲羽球世錦賽，日本隊在女雙賽事上包辦了冠、亞軍。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n今年羽球世錦賽的女雙，日本隊由松本麻佑/永原和可那、福島由紀/廣田彩花，包辦了冠亞軍。在頒獎儀式上，體育館內奏起了日本國歌並升起了三面國旗。<br />\n<br />\n但這場景卻讓許多大陸網友崩潰，微博上許多人紛紛留言說「出於民族情感，怎麼可以讓日本國旗在南京升起來」、「厭惡這面旗子」、「喪權辱國的感覺」、「我覺得作為『獎勵』，應該帶日本女雙去南京大屠殺紀念館參觀一下，了解他們祖輩曾經在南京幹過的齷齪事」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1477691-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1477691-XXL.jpg&h=6618baf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲頒獎典禮時，升起了三面日本國旗，讓許多大陸網友崩潰了。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n不過還是有不少大陸網友表示，中國大陸國家隊技不如人，「國羽應該認真反思了，到底是哪裡出了錯？！在南京升起日本國旗實在是一種諷刺」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=412741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D412741&d=oOZMTXzW7vfu8itstuCjnTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=34d6cc3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D412741&h=fd6d914e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=412741</a>"},{"pid":"37f8bcf5eef9e22873683bfc0f7a9a0360fb2473","tid":769262,"uid":171786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a563ebd4ac6d37f3e80598db9a36142931705553","tid":769262,"uid":51129,"like":187,"dislike":2,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3816a11233d1434074364c0a32c7826631bc1ca4","tid":769262,"uid":33796,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"怨婦咁"},{"pid":"0959ff4d7aa891b3d797bff7fb7c9f1dda0f0d31","tid":769262,"uid":95497,"like":238,"dislike":0,"score":238,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">應該帶中國人去長春參觀一下，了解他們祖輩曾經在長春幹過的齷齪事」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588583f7a480b70939eda7851983ce372175112f","tid":769262,"uid":135408,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"贏國輸左就發賴?"},{"pid":"323e3a0c3d41b099b1db7fbca2f14d727d664e4d","tid":769262,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0743e31f9d5edc7cbe371f2a5aafe3bd0d371f2f","tid":769262,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"日本x3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c312d8aefe6360e2b09740232e508d0d368bb7a0","tid":769262,"uid":52006,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:11:39.000Z